Project Description
This is a open source theme designed by using Twitter Bootstap. It is open source for the NopCommerce community and it will be open source for all next release.

NopRoot is a free open source theme designed by Brainstation-23 using TwitterBootstrap-3.2 for the NopCommerce community and it will be open source for all future releases. Demo : http://nopbs.com.rose.arvixe.com
Supported Versions: nopCommerce 3.20 , nopCommerce 3.30 , nopCommerce 3.40
